OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777126305
OL,3,CAlleged associate of Manchester
OL,4,Csynagogue attacker denies terror
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FAn alleged associate of the Manchester
OL,8,Fsynagogue attacker has denied driving
OL,9,Fhim to the UK's Defence Academy to
OL,10,Fcarry out hostile reconnaissance.
OL,12,FMohammad Bashir, 31, pleaded not
OL,13,Fguilty on 24 April to preparation of
OL,14,Fterrorist acts and three counts of
OL,15,Fdisseminating terrorist publications
OL,16,Fon WhatsApp on dates in November and
OL,17,FDecember 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
