PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777126305
OL,3,CAlleged associate of Manchester
OL,4,Csynagogue attacker denies terror
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FThe first charges alleges he drove
OL,8,FJihad Al-Shamie to the UK Defence
OL,9,FAcademy in Shrivenham, Oxfordshire, on
OL,10,F14 August 2025 to carry out hostile
OL,11,Freconnaissance of the location, weeks
OL,12,Fbefore the synagogue attack.
OL,14,FHe did so "with the intention of
OL,15,Fassisting Jihad Al-Shamie to commit
OL,16,Facts of terrorism", the charge states.
OL,18,FThe assistance allegedly provided by
OL,19,FBashir was not in relation to the
OL,20,Fattack on the Heaton Park Hebrew
OL,21,FSynagogue in Crumpsall, on 2 October.
OL,26,@vD@KOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
