PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777126305
OL,3,CAlleged associate of Manchester
OL,4,Csynagogue attacker denies terror
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FWorshippers Melvin Cravitz, 66, died
OL,8,Falong with Adrian Daulby, 53, were
OL,9,Fkilled after 35-year-old Al-Shamie, a
OL,10,FSyrian-born UK citizen, drove his Kia
OL,11,FPicanto into the gates of the
OL,12,Fsynagogue and began attacking with a
OL,13,Fknife, wearing a fake suicide belt.
OL,15,FHe was shot dead by armed police as he
OL,16,Fcarried out the attack.
OL,18,FBashir was arrested at Manchester
OL,19,FAirport on 27 November.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
