PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777126305
OL,3,CAlleged associate of Manchester
OL,4,Csynagogue attacker denies terror
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FHe faces a four-week trial from 6 July
OL,8,Fat Manchester Crown Court before Mrs
OL,9,FJustice Cheema-Grubb.
OL,11,FThe defendant, of Shaftsbury Road,
OL,12,FManchester, was remanded into custody
OL,13,Fahead of a pre-trial review at the Old
OL,14,FBailey on 5 June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
